          .signup-content__input-location
          -# = f.text_field :security_number, placeholder: '  カード背面４桁もしくは３桁の番号', class:"input__default"
           = text_field_tag "cvc", "", class: "cvc", placeholder: "カード背面3~4桁の番号", maxlength: "4", id: "cvc"
          .signup__wrapper__registration__form__code
            %i.fas.fa-question-circle カード裏面の番号とは？
